message.text:
𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑯𝑼𝑵𝑻 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒌𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝑪𝒐𝒎𝒎𝒊𝒕𝒕𝒆𝒆 ☁️🎈

Our deepest gratitude to the TamHunt 2025 working committee for making this event a soaring success! Together, we flew higher than Pampanga’s hot air balloons, the very inspiration behind our theme. 🪂🍃

You turned TamHunt into an unforgettable sky-high moment. With every ounce of effort and passion, we didn’t just reach the skies… we broke through them. ✨☝️

Palaging 𝑪𝒀𝑪𝒊𝒃𝒐𝒍 sa 𝐡𝐢𝐦𝐏𝐀𝐌𝐏𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐝—hanggang sa muli! 🌟

Maraming salamat, Y'ers! 💫

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption by Stephanie Ashley Buenaventura 
Publication Materials by Janelle Tañedo, LJ Rocha, and Shanley Gungon

message.text:
𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑯𝑼𝑵𝑻 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒌𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝑪𝒐𝒎𝒎𝒊𝒕𝒕𝒆𝒆 ☁️🎈

Our deepest gratitude to the TamHunt 2025 working committee for making this event a soaring success! Together, we flew higher than Pampanga’s hot air balloons, the very inspiration behind our theme. 🪂🍃

You turned TamHunt into an unforgettable sky-high moment. With every ounce of effort and passion, we didn’t just reach the skies… we broke through them. ✨☝️

Palaging 𝑪𝒀𝑪𝒊𝒃𝒐𝒍 sa 𝐡𝐢𝐦𝐏𝐀𝐌𝐏𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐝—hanggang sa muli! 🌟

Maraming salamat, Y'ers! 💫

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption by Stephanie Ashley Buenaventura 
Publication Materials by Janelle Tañedo, LJ Rocha, and Shanley Gungon

𝘚𝘢 𝘪𝘭𝘢𝘭𝘪𝘮 𝘯𝘨 𝘬𝘢𝘮𝘢𝘺 𝘯𝘢 𝘣𝘢𝘬𝘢𝘭, 𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰-𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰𝘯𝘨 𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘪𝘨 𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘱𝘪𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘢𝘩𝘪𝘮𝘪𝘬—𝘩𝘶𝘸𝘢𝘨 𝘯𝘢 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘩𝘢𝘺𝘢𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘮𝘢𝘶𝘭𝘪𝘵 𝘱𝘢. 

Inaanyayahan ng IAS Student Council ang lahat na makilahok sa "Sa Ilalim ng Kamay na Bakal: Paggunita sa Batas Militar", isang serye ng mga aktibidad na magpapaalala ng katotohanan at magpapatibay ng ating paninindigan: 𝗡𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗿 𝗮𝗴𝗮𝗶𝗻.

Abangan ngayong Setyembre!

Mag-signup para sa Political Forum dito:
https://events.teams.microsoft.com/event/a32365dc-c1d0-4c79-8ffb-17d5ec41ada3@80a45edc-d5ee-46e0-9d75-37c47be9b7cc

Kasama ang FEU Communication Society.

#NeverAgainNeverForget
#FightHistoricalDistortion
#TamarawsRemember

Uunahin. Nalalapitan. Aasikasuhin.
#SerbisyongFirstKa #IASSC79

𝘚𝘢 𝘪𝘭𝘢𝘭𝘪𝘮 𝘯𝘨 𝘬𝘢𝘮𝘢𝘺 𝘯𝘢 𝘣𝘢𝘬𝘢𝘭, 𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰-𝘭𝘪𝘣𝘰𝘯𝘨 𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘪𝘨 𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘱𝘪𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘢𝘩𝘪𝘮𝘪𝘬—𝘩𝘶𝘸𝘢𝘨 𝘯𝘢 𝘯𝘢𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘩𝘢𝘺𝘢𝘢𝘯𝘨 𝘮𝘢𝘶𝘭𝘪𝘵 𝘱𝘢.
